    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Welcome to the world of <i>William's Curse</i>!</strong><br>You wake up as Emily, a young girl trapped in a strange and crazy school. To escape, you must collect notebooks on every floor, escape from teachers, and face William — a bad teacher who is controlling everyone’s minds.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each floor has different subjects and psychopath teachers. On the last floor, you’ll have to beat William to save yourself, your friend Helpscreen, and the school staff.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game has different difficulty levels:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Lil Puss Mode</strong>: Great for new players. No threats, lots of light, and you can explore without danger.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Boi Difficulty</strong>: Simple questions and slow teachers. Good for learning the basics.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Default Difficulty</strong>: A normal challenge. Questions are a bit harder but not too crazy.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Brainiac Difficulty</strong>: Very hard! Tough questions, fast teachers, and special achievements for beating each level.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hardcore Mode</strong>: Choose any difficulty, but you have to finish all five floors without losing once to move on.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i><strong>Jump into the game — Emily’s life is in your hands!</strong></i></h2></li></ul>",
